name: Gravity isn't real
description:
You are a cat that jumps over spikes in a dungeon to get to the delicious catfood!

Move around using AD keys or left and right arrow. To change gravity press W top go up and S to go down.

The game has 4 levels so it is a very short game.

I think that I followed the theme on a decent level.

Thank you for playing "Gravity isn't real)
